Or look me up in game and I'll be happy to talk to you about it more.<br>
<br>
Incidentally, another amazing quaddng spot around that level is the ulthorks in easetern wastes. Profitable and as you say, insane experience all the way up to your mid 40's.<br>
<br>
Safe hunting,<br>
~<br>
